{
  "stem": "11472.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He-- in fact, he signed it over to him that if he saves his grandson, the forest would belong to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My Uncle Nisel was friends with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he came and he said to him, listen, I'm looking for a place to hide my family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, look, there is another grotto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not too far from here, there is a grotto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's on the land that belongs to the priests.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They called it Popowa Yama.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That the-- it belongs to the priests.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was like a ditch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "A yama is a ditch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He says, I think there is a grotto there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So he and my Uncle Schloime and, and the grandson of Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH] Dodek and Mendel Dodek took a lot of rope.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they went to look where this grotto is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In order to get into this grotto, you had to go with your feet first and with your hand up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you had to slide in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was mud.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was at-- it was-- a hill was, like, was surrounding it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was a big ditch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that you had to slide in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They slid in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They had to crawl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyway, they came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they found a place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In fact, they were walking and walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They couldn't find an end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they found water in that grotto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dark, pitch black.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't see nothing in high places, in low places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, they found a, a home for us, a haven for us. 39 people was the Dodek family, the Stermer family, the [NON-ENGLISH] family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] came in with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
